<plot>Documentary on theater director Antunes Filho, his five decades working with theater, and his work method. There are also some scenes from his plays. The series is divided in 6 episodes: 1 - As Origens de um Artista (The Origins of an Artist) 2 - A Década das Transgressões (The Transgressions Decade) 3 - Desafios de um Tempo Duro (Challenges of a Hard Time) 4 - Mestre e Discípulos (Master and Pupils) 5 - A Poética do Mal (Poetics of Evil) 6 - O Método (The Method)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?405116</url></doc>
